eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.CalculationModelSpecification
Specification of a model used in an energy assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the model. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.GrossEnergyAssessment
Gross energy yield assessment.
Attributes: results (list[Result]): Gross energy yield results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.Result
Set of results for an element of an energy assessment.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. assessment_period (AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is 'lifetime'. dimensions (Optional[tuple[ResultsDimension(StrEnum), ...]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[tuple[UnionType[float, int, str], ...], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. Default is []. wind_resource_assessment_basis (Optional[WindResourceAssessmentBasis]): Measurement wind resource assessment basis for the scenario. Default is None. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (Optional[TurbineWindResourceAssessment]): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. Default is None. gross_energy_assessment (GrossEnergyAssessment): Gross energy yield assessment. plant_performance_assessment (PlantPerformanceAssessment): Plant performance assessment including net energy results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.TurbineWindResourceAssessment

Attributes: turbine_wind_resource_results (list[Result]): Assessment results at the turbine location(s). wind_spatial_models (list[CalculationModelSpecification]): Wind spatial models used in the assessment. uncertainty_assessment (Optional[UncertaintyAssessment]): Turbine wind resource uncertainty assessment. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.WindResourceAssessmentBasis

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: name (str): Name of the wind farm. label (Optional[str]): Abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. wind_farm_restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.
